What are your opinions on drones and cryptocurrency? Join Tech + Social Impact for its virtual tech talk, Ethics in the Cyberspace, on Tuesday 4/5 from 4-5PM to learn more and discuss these topics with none other than the amazing Nick Weaver!  We will also be giving away multiple AirPods! 

Zoom link: tinyurl.com/ethicsincyberspace
RSVP here: https://forms.gle/JHd2inVnj2ewqpYr7

We hope to see you there! 🙂
